main event: Six star-like objects, white in color, in a straight line formation, flew in a southern direction at a rapid rate of speed, dimmed in their intensity of light for three seconds to the east.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 31 seconds., The objects were observed flying in a straight line., The objects dimmed in intensity before continuing., The investigation suggested the objects were probably caused by three jet aircraft., The report was part of Project Blue Book.
